    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Indeed jQuery.trigger will not work here since jQuery.trigger only triggers events that were registered through jQuery event handling.\n\nYou might have better results by using this: https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/Events/Creating_and_triggering_events#Triggering_built-in_events\n\nOr any non jQuery way to trigger a click. Try this and if it does not work you will have to create a [custom widget](https://community.algolia.com/instantsearch.js/documentation/#custom-widgets) and use the [helper](https://community.algolia.com/algoliasearch-helper-js/) inside it.\n",
